    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects meticulous care, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically uncompromising and aesthetically superior, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection.",
